My ETL plain for Atlanta Library Periodicals:

Extract
    Load periodicals.cdv into pandas
There are 2 csv file types and they need to be linked in some way:
    periodical issues
    periodical titles

Understand the data
    titles.id uniquely identifies a periodical.
    issues.title_id references the parent periodical.
    titles contains publication metadata (publisher, ISSN, start/end dates).
    issues contains issue-specific metadata (publication date, pages, description).

Transform
    Merge titles with issues
    Use periodical id to match records
    Extract volume from description 
    Extract issue number from description
    Inspect columns
    Rename columns to match ask from Java team
    Remove duplicate records
    Convert publishing_date into month/date/year format
    Keep ISSN values
    Keep publisher
    Keep publication date 
    Handle any missing values
    Rename columns if Java team requires different names

Load 
    Export cleaned DataFrame to JSON

Java Team Columns Requested
    Title of perodical
    Publisher
    ISSN --> for periodical not issue specific
    Place --> locations associated with periodical
    Issue publication date--> ex: mar 2023, april 2023
    Pages --> in issues
    Volume #--> find in descption for issues
    Issue # --> find in descption for issues
    Periodical Publishing date-> lastest publication year or check description(if the publication is active or not)
    
   
  
    JSON file schema:
    fields:"
    name:title
    type: string
    descption: "title of periodical"

    name:publisher
    type: string
    descption: "publisher of periodical"

    name:ISSN
    type: string
    descption: ISSN of periodical"

    name:location (place)
    type: string
    descption: "location associated with periodical"

    name:publication date (date)
    type: date
    descption: "issue publication date"

    name:pages
    type: integer
    descption: "number of pages in this issue"

    name:volume (description)
    type: integer
    descption: "volume of issue"

    name:issue number (description)
    type: integer
    descption: "issue number"

   

